# Day 2: Rock Paper Scissors

```elixir
Mix.install([:kino])
```

## Part 1

```elixir
input = Kino.Input.textarea("Input")
```

```elixir
score = %{
  {"A", "X"} => 3 + 1,
  {"A", "Y"} => 6 + 2,
  {"A", "Z"} => 0 + 3,
  {"B", "X"} => 0 + 1,
  {"B", "Y"} => 3 + 2,
  {"B", "Z"} => 6 + 3,
  {"C", "X"} => 6 + 1,
  {"C", "Y"} => 0 + 2,
  {"C", "Z"} => 3 + 3
}

input
|> Kino.Input.read()
|> String.split("\n")
|> Enum.map(&String.split/1)
|> Enum.map(fn [x, y] -> score[{x, y}] end)
|> Enum.sum()
```
